      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I'm a bit sad to let this one go, but it's time for a new home. This beauty is in absolute showroom condition\u2014it literally looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! Not a single scratch or dent to be found anywhere. It\u2019s been totally pampered since day one and is ready for its next big adventure. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
