    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing impeccable mechanical integrity and aesthetic preservation. At its heart lies the S54B32 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six, featuring a 11.5:1 compression ratio and individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission. This example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by original factory-spec bushings and a pristine limited-slip differential. The exterior finish remains in showroom state, free of rock chips or oxidation. A true driver\u2019s specimen with a documented service history that validates its exceptional pedigree.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
