      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and always tucked away in the garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the full retail sticker shock, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
