      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the high-pressure VANOS system has been meticulously calibrated, and the rear subframe has undergone proactive reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The factory-spec limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution, while the suspension geometry remains true with zero bushing deflection. This is a collector-grade specimen with original VIN-matching panels and a pristine undercarriage, representing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering.",
